# AcademicianClaw — Plugin Memory Directory
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# RULE: This directory contains EXAMPLE TEMPLATES ONLY.
#       Real live memory files live at the workspace root: /memory/
#       Examples are committed so new users get a starting point.
#       Live data is never committed — it is personal to each faculty member.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Exclude all .md files (live runtime data)
*.md

# Keep committed example templates
!*.md.example

# Keep this gitignore
!.gitignore

# Subdirectory rules — same policy applies recursively
# (Git applies parent .gitignore rules to subdirs by default)
